.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, hip-hop, house, metal
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, rock-climbing, singing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, dunhill, davidoff, montecristo
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, roller, trike
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is the fan of metal##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the fan of country is between the person driving the roller and the fan of house##2
13. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | coffee     | fanta        | iced-tea      |
