.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-13::.
There 4 different types of food: begoniarot, kale, plum, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: begoniad-games, fishing, gardening, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, fantasy, sports
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, tea, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, snake, turtle
